{"tid":2357380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙控削減基層員工2020年度花紅分發上限22%","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:26:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a6b9a0ee5bb7ebad4826a7356caff881684a30","tid":2357380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569202-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569202-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=56842055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569202-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=040b5eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569202-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n滙控向全球基層員工發出通知，裁減2020年度花紅分發上限22%。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人回覆查詢時指，去年外在環境充滿挑戰，集團業績受到影響，去年第3季列帳基準稅後利潤減少62%，經調整稅前利潤減少44%。集團會調整6至8職級員工2020年制度化評分模式花紅，考慮到有關員工在這困難時期的努力付出，總體薪酬大致上仍持平，或有些些微上升，希望員工諒解。"}]}